---
// Scene 2: The story hook — what problem does Percor solve?
---

<section class="py-20 md:py-32 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 lg:px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p data-reveal class="text-accent font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Problemet</p>
      <h2 data-reveal class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-text leading-tight">
        Du har en bedrift å drive.<br />
        <span class="text-text-light">Ikke et klesskap å fylle.</span>
      </h2>
      <p data-reveal class="mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-text-secondary leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Å finne riktig arbeidstøy, få logoen på plass, og sørge for at alt matcher — det tar tid du ikke har.
        Vi tar den jobben.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Three pain points that flow into solutions -->
    <div data-reveal-stagger class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-16">
      <div class="relative p-8 rounded-2xl bg-bg-alt border border-border">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M21 21l-5.197-5.197m0 0A7.5 7.5 0 105.196 15.803a7.5 7.5 0 0010.607 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-text mb-2">Uoversiktlig marked</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">Hundrevis av leverandører, tusenvis av produkter. Hvem leverer kvalitet? Hvem kan du stole på?</p>
        <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-border">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary">Vi har gjort jobben for deg →</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-text-light mt-1">6 nøye utvalgte merkevarer, én kontaktperson</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative p-8 rounded-2xl bg-bg-alt border border-border">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M9.53 16.122a3 3 0 00-5.78 1.128 2.25 2.25 0 01-2.4 2.245 4.5 4.5 0 008.4-2.245c0-.399-.078-.78-.22-1.128zm0 0a15.998 15.998 0 003.388-1.62m-5.043-.025a15.994 15.994 0 011.622-3.395m3.42 3.42a15.995 15.995 0 004.764-4.648l3.876-5.814a1.151 1.151 0 00-1.597-1.597L14.146 6.32a15.996 15.996 0 00-4.649 4.764m3.42 3.42a6.776 6.776 0 00-3.42-3.42" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-text mb-2">Logo, trykk, profil</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">Klærne er bare starten. Broderi, trykk, design — alt skal stemme. Og det haster alltid.</p>
        <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-border">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary">Alt under ett tak →</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-text-light mt-1">Klær + trykk + design = én leveranse</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative p-8 rounded-2xl bg-bg-alt border border-border">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M8.25 18.75a1.5 1.5 0 01-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m3 0h6m-9 0H3.375a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V14.25m17.25 4.5a1.5 1.5 0 01-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m3 0h1.125c.621 0 1.129-.504 1.09-1.124a17.902 17.902 0 00-3.213-9.193 2.056 2.056 0 00-1.58-.86H14.25M16.5 18.75h-2.25m0-11.177v-.958c0-.568-.422-1.048-.987-1.106a48.554 48.554 0 00-10.026 0 1.106 1.106 0 00-.987 1.106v7.635m12-6.677v6.677m0 4.5v-4.5m0 0h-12" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-text mb-2">Bil, butikk, messe</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">Profilen din stopper ikke ved klærne. Biler, vinduer, bannere, skilt — alt skal henge sammen.</p>
        <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-border">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary">Vi dekker alt →</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-text-light mt-1">Foliering, storformat, fasadeskilt</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
